OL,6,FHe worked with Mirgent Shahu, 33, from
OL,7,FSutton Coldfield, and Robert Ball, 60,
OL,8,Ffrom Cheshire who are in prison for
OL,9,Ftheir involvement in the operation.
OL,11,FThe container containing the cocaine
OL,12,Foriginally arrived at London Gateway
OL,13,Fport from Ecuador.
OL,15,FHere, the gang did not know it, but
OL,16,FBorder Force officers were working
OL,17,Fwith the NCA who found cocaine
OL,18,Fpackages in the roof.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/6
