OL,6,FA few days later, Ball, contacted the
OL,7,Fshipping firm to ask them to release
OL,8,Fthe four containers, including the one
OL,9,Fthat contained drugs.
OL,11,FHe arranged transport for the
OL,12,Fcontainers to Coventry, but did not
OL,13,Fknow that the NCA were watching his
OL,14,Fsteps.
OL,16,FAli, Ball and Shahu met in Kings Heath
OL,17,Fon the morning of the 15th April 2022
OL,18,Fto make final arrangements.
